dataDictionary.Title: PDS4 Data Dictionary
dataDictionary.Description: This document is a dump of the contents of the PDS4 Data Dictionary

class.title: LEISA_Instrument_Parameters
class.description: The Lucy LRalph LEISA class that contains the instrument specific attributes relevant to the labeled data product.

class.title: LLORRI_Instrument_Parameters
class.description: The Lucy LORRI instrument class that contains instrument specific attributes relevant to the labeled data product.

class.title: LRalph_Instrument_Common_Parameters
class.description: The Lucy LRalph instrument class that contains the common (LEISA and MVIC) instrument specific attributes relevant to the labeled data product.

class.title: Lucy_Observation_Planning
class.description: The Lucy Mission observation planning class and attributes describe the observation planning information needed to understand the planned spacecraft observations.

class.title: Lucy_Observation_Time_Information
class.description: Lucy Mission observation identification and timing information.

class.title: Lucy_Product_Information
class.description: The Lucy Mission class that contains attributes specific to the labeled data product.

class.title: Lucy_Target_List
class.description: The Lucy Mission class that contains the target list of potential targets in a given observation.

class.title: MVIC_Instrument_Parameters
class.description: The Lucy LRalph MVIC class that contains the instrument specific attributes relevant to the labeled data product.

attribute.title: leisa_atrack_num_channels

attribute.title: leisa_atrack_start_channel
attribute.description: LEISA along track start channel

attribute.title: leisa_fpe_ir_temperature
attribute.description: LEISA FPE IR Temperature (TBR)

attribute.description: LEISA cross track start row.

attribute.title: attached_sync_marker_dec

attribute.description: Attached Sync Marker, hexidecimal representation.

attribute.title: calibration_lamp_level_1
attribute.description: The Digital Number (DN) setting for calibration lamp one.

attribute.title: fpe_drop_frames
attribute.description: Number of FPE drop frames (TBR).

attribute.description: The cross track start row from the high speed header.

attribute.description: The Lralph observation acquisition start block address.

attribute.description: Blackbody state (TBR)

attribute.description: Calibration state (TBR)

attribute.title: m4_filament_setting
attribute.description: Filament setting (TBR)

attribute.title: mce_end_postion
attribute.description: The MCE start position (TBR), units TBD

attribute.title: mce_scan_rate
attribute.description: The MCE scan rate (TBR).

attribute.title: mce_start_postion
attribute.description: The MCE start position (TBR), units TBD

attribute.title: playback_bad_pixel_mask_status
attribute.description: Status of the bad pixel map, true or false

attribute.title: playback_end
attribute.description: Playback science header timstamp of the last m4 packet used in spacecraft clock seconds.
attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: playback_header_type
attribute.description: Playback header type

PermissibleValue.valueMeaning: LIESA CDS mode is selected for the current observation (TBR)
CDS is not used in the current LEISA observation (TBR)
MVIC is selected for the current observation (TBR)
Other values to be filled in. This is a placeholder.(TBR)

attribute.title: playback_start
attribute.description: Playback science header timstamp of the first m4 packet used in spacecraft clock seconds.
attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: playback_truncation_status
attribute.description: Status of the truncation enabled, true or false

attribute.title: scan_row_pixels
attribute.description: The number of pixels in the scan row.

attribute.title: test_pattern_setting
attribute.description: The instrument test pattern setting, 0 is science, 1 is test pattern.

attribute.title: xsum_error_flag_status
attribute.description: Xsum flag indicating if there are errors in the stored data packet, true or false

attribute.title: instrument_side
attribute.description: The Lucy elctronics side.

PermissibleValue.valueMeaning: The "A" electronics side. This is the default electronics side.
The "B" electronics side. This is the redundant fault protection side used in case of an error on the "A" side.

attribute.description: The status of the L'TES instrument.

attribute.description: The Lucy Mission segment

PermissibleValue.valueMeaning: The Cruise_1 Lucy Mission segment from date XXXX to date XXX.
The EGA_1 (Earth Gravity Assist) Lucy Mission segment from date XXXX to date XXX.

attribute.title: ttcam_status
attribute.description: The status of the TTCAM instrument.

attribute.title: visit_name
attribute.description: The Lucy Mission trojan asteroid visit name.

attribute.title: mid_ephemeris_time
attribute.description: The middle time of the observation in ephemeris time, seconds past J2000, TDB.
attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: mid_sclk
attribute.description: The Lucy spacecraft clock (SCLK) time (in seconds) at the mid-time of the observation.
attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: mid_sclk_string
attribute.description: The middle time of the observation in Lucy spacecraft clock string partition/SSSSSSSSSS-PPPPP, where S is seconds and P are ticks in units of 1/66535 of a second.

attribute.title: mid_utc
attribute.description: The middle time of the observation in ISO UTC format "YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS.sss"

attribute.title: mid_utc_doy
attribute.description: The middle time of the observation in ISO DOY format, YYYY-DOYTHH:MM:SS.sss

attribute.title: mid_utc_jd
attribute.description: The middle time of the observation in Julian day format,
attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: observation_complete
attribute.description: The Lucy Mission observation is complete.

attribute.description: The Lucy Mission observation identifier.

attribute.title: observation_id_count
attribute.description: The Lucy Mission observation identifier counter. This number increments by 1 with each planned observation sequence.

attribute.title: observation_missing_packets
attribute.description: The number of missing packets in the observation. The best data quality has no missing packets.

attribute.title: start_sclk

attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: stop_sclk

attribute.unitId: day, hr, julian day, microseconds, min, ms, ns, s, yr

attribute.title: internal_product_version_id
attribute.description: The Lucy pipeline internal data processing version number. This number is likely to be grater than the PDS version number given in the version_id attribute in the Observation_Area.
